stories.title: Sneak peek of what we're doing!
stories.description: What if you could have electricity anywhere there was sunlight? What if the charge on your phone could last for weeks, the poorest, most remote homes in the world could have electric home lighting, and adding a USB charge outlet was as simple as slapping a sticker onto a sunlit wall? All of these are becoming possible thanks to microsolar: small solar panels that are small and cheap enough to go anywhere.

stories.title: Sneak peek of what we're doing!
stories.description: We also have to apologise to you, because we will not meet our shipping deadline - and this means we will deliver your units in the second week of May. We are very sorry, and believe us we have worked hard to remain within our scheduling. But we decided to make the Charge even better than originally planned, and we felt that you and all of our future partners would appreciate that even if it means counting down a few more weeks before holding the sun in your hands.

stories.title: Packing and delivering to you!
stories.description: Here at Little Sun HQ, our team is busily getting the Little Sun Charges packed (all eco materials!) and on their merry way to you, just in time for the sunny weekend. We very much hope you enjoy your Charge.
